OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FThe Green Party has stormed to victory
OL,8,Fin the Gorton and Denton by-election,
OL,9,Fsetting a number of historic firsts
OL,10,Fand causing a crisis for Labour.
OL,12,FBut, alongside their victory, there
OL,13,Fhave been some accusations that voters
OL,14,Fbreached electoral law, with people
OL,15,Fpartaking in so-called "family voting".
OL,17,FCries of dodgy practices and unfair
OL,18,Ftreatment are often made by the losing
OL,19,Fparties in elections, but this time
OL,20,Fthey came from an election observer
OL,21,Fgroup.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
