OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772216417
OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FDemocracy Volunteers has claimed the
OL,8,Fby-election was rife with what they
OL,9,Fcalled "family voting," which
OL,10,Finfluences how people conduct their
OL,11,Fvote.
OL,13,FThe Green Party's Hannah Spencer won
OL,14,Fthe seat by a considerable margin, and
OL,15,Fthere has been no evidence yet that
OL,16,Ffamily voting benefited a single party
OL,17,For impacted the result of the election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
