OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FThe chair of Reform UK, David Bull,
OL,8,Ftold BBC Radio 4 on Friday that the
OL,9,Fpractice was "illegal" but when asked
OL,10,Fif it made a difference in the
OL,11,Felection, he said "probably not".
OL,13,FWhat is family voting?
OL,15,FAlthough the term family voting has
OL,16,Fsurged in Google searches in the past
OL,17,F24 hours, it is not a legal or widely
OL,18,Frecognised term.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
