OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FGoogle Trends data shows the phrase
OL,8,Fhad relatively little interest prior
OL,9,Fto the Gorton and Denton by-election.
OL,11,FSome politicians use it as a shorthand
OL,12,Fway to refer to the issue of multiple
OL,13,Fpeople using a voting booth at the
OL,14,Fsame time, or someone being pressured
OL,15,Fto vote for a candidate while in a
OL,16,Fpolling booth by someone outside it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
