OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FIt is also the preferred term used by
OL,8,FDemocracy Volunteers, the group that
OL,9,Fraised the issue during the vote count
OL,10,Fon election night, to describe the
OL,11,Fissue of multiple people entering a
OL,12,Fpolling booth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
