OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FDemocracy Volunteers is a small non-
OL,8,Fgovernmental organisation that
OL,9,Fobserves elections around the UK and
OL,10,FEurope. They have operated for more
OL,11,Fthan ten years and are funded by
OL,12,Fgroups including the Joseph Rowntree
OL,13,FReform Trust, an independent non-
OL,14,Fcharitable trust that pushes for
OL,15,Fdemocratic and political reform.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
