OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772216417
OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FThey have been permitted by the
OL,8,FElectoral Commission to observe some
OL,9,Felections in the UK. They say they
OL,10,F"maintain strict impartiality and
OL,11,Frequire our observers to abide by UK
OL,12,Fand international standards".
OL,14,FThe phrase family voting is not used
OL,15,Fin law, but it is an offence under the
OL,16,FBallot Secrecy Act to enter a polling
OL,17,Fbooth with another person.
OL,19,FIt is also an offence to attempt to
OL,20,Finfluence someone's vote while they
OL,21,Fare in the polling booth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
