OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FSecret ballot voting is a core part of
OL,8,Fmost democracies and is seen as one of
OL,9,Fthe most important principles that
OL,10,Fmaintains a free society.
OL,12,FElection monitors are often quick to
OL,13,Fcall out when they believe the
OL,14,Fsanctity of the secret ballot has been
OL,15,Fcompromised.
OL,17,FWas it an issue during the by-election?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
