OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772216417
OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FThe group said their observers
OL,8,Fattended several polling stations and
OL,9,Fsaw family voting in 15 of the 22
OL,10,Fpolling stations observed, 32 cases in
OL,11,Ftotal, with nine cases in one polling
OL,12,Fstation alone. The team observed a
OL,13,Fsample of 545 voters casting their
OL,14,Fvote, meaning 12% of those voters
OL,15,Fobserved either caused or were
OL,16,Faffected by family voting.
OL,18,FBut this statement was quickly
OL,19,Frebuffed by Manchester City Council,
OL,20,Fwhich said they had "seen no such
OL,21,Fissues".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772216417
OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FThey said: "If Democracy Volunteers
OL,8,Fwere so concerned about alleged issues
OL,9,Fthey could and should have raised them
OL,10,Fwith us during polling hours so that
OL,11,Fimmediate action could be taken.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FThey added: "It is extremely
OL,19,Fdisappointing that Democracy
OL,20,FVolunteers have waited until after
OL,21,Fpolls have closed to make such claims."
OL,26,@zD@MOU}D@gO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
