OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FReform UK leader Nigel Farage said the
OL,8,Felection "was a victory for sectarian
OL,9,Fvoting and cheating," but the Greens
OL,10,Fsaid the claims were "an attempt to
OL,11,Fundermine the democratic result and is
OL,12,Fstraight out of the Trump playbook."
OL,14,FGreen leader Zack Polanski told BBC
OL,15,FNewsnight he would back a probe into
OL,16,Fthe issue if it was recommended by
OL,17,Fauthorities.
OL,19,FLabour Party Chair Anna Turley also
OL,20,Ftold Newsnight the claims were
OL,21,F"worrying and concerning".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
