PN,30714
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1772216417
OL,3,CWhat is family voting and was it an
OL,4,Cissue in the Gorton and Denton by-
OL,5,Celection?
OL,7,FThe Electoral Commission said it was
OL,8,F"aware of concerns raised over family
OL,9,Fvoting," and they encouraged anyone
OL,10,Fwith knowledge of any offences to go
OL,11,Fto the police.
OL,13,FYou can hear Talking Politics wherever
OL,14,Fyou get your podcasts, including Apple
OL,15,FPodcasts and Spotify, and watch every
OL,16,Fepisode on YouTube and ITVX.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
